{"type":"message","id":"18309827","parentId":"412a4374","timestamp":"2026-06-02T03:35:59.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The user is asking about which API key is being used. Let me just show them the structure of the models.json file - I shouldn't expose the actual key value, but I can show the configuration.\n\nKey 配置文件在 `~/.openclaw/agents/main/models.json`，结构如下（值已打码）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"minimax\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1\",\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"authHeader\": true,\n      \"apiKey\": \"eyJhbG…)***\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"contextWindow\": 200000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192,\n          \"reasoning\": false\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"minimax-cn\": { ... },\n    \"openrouter\": { ... },\n    \"arcee\": { ... },\n    \"codex\": { ... },\n    \"gemini\": { ... }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**当前用的 key：minimax（minimaxi.com）**\n\n要查看明文的话，你自己 `cat ~/.openclaw/agents/main/models.json` 就行 — 我就不直接打明文 key 了，避免日志留痕。\n\n需要切换 key 或看完整配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":3963,"output":285,"cacheRead":47566,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780371336770,"responseId":"066d8289097dd6419482070a91722c63"}}
