{"type":"message","id":"479fb15a","parentId":"d50d1e43","timestamp":"2026-06-02T09:04:44.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The user is asking whether opencli (presumably clawhub or openclaw CLI) needs to install skills separately when the command line has already installed them. This seems to be a question about whether skills installed via the command line tool also work in the openclaw ecosystem.\n\nLet me check if there's an opencli tool, and verify if skills installed via the CLI are recognized."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e3l7a2xqwv9w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which clawhub && clawhub list 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":52002,"output":115,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52231,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780391072599,"responseId":"066dcfa0445faf575b0bab4f3e021e36"}}
{"type":"message","id":"43a66301","parentId":"479fb15a","timestamp":"2026-06-02T09:04:45.634Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e3l7a2xqwv9w_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/halei/.npm-global/bin/clawhub\ncontext-engine  2.1.1\nself-improving-agent  3.0.21"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":904,"aggregated":"/home/halei/.npm-global/bin/clawhub\ncontext-engine  2.1.1\nself-improving-agent  3.0.21","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780391085632}}
{"type":"message","id":"87c31e03","parentId":"43a66301","timestamp":"2026-06-02T09:04:56.035Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes, clawhub 已安装并能识别刚才装的 `self-improving-agent` (3.0.21)。`context-engine` 也是之前装的。\n\n**答案：不需要。** 通过 `clawhub install` 装的 skill 会自动：\n1. 下载到 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<name>/`\n2. OpenClaw 启动时自动加载并出现在可用 skill 列表\n\n刚才你装完 self-improving-agent 后，我在 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving-agent/` 看到目录已经创建 — 这就是 openclaw 用的标准 skill 路径。\n\n**唯一的注意事项：**\n- 如果 OpenClaw 已经在运行，新装的 skill **需要重启 Gateway** 才会被主会话识别（因为 skill 列表是启动时加载的）\n- 用 `gateway restart` 即可\n- 重启后 OpenClaw 会自动 ping 当前 session，不需要你手动操作\n\n需要我重启一下让 self-improving-agent 生效吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":63,"output":201,"cacheRead":52217,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52481,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780391085679,"responseId":"066dcfae2a7744d689e4a2ebada3d692"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8b9925f","parentId":"87c31e03","timestamp":"2026-06-02T11:38:29.788Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6ed845dcccb4c01c9fe4c146d39\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-06-02 19:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n重启吧， 我的意思是 opencli 这个 cli工具需不需要在安装skill进行配合"}],"timestamp":1780400309763}}
