{"type":"message","id":"3304e14e","parentId":"03e7df17","timestamp":"2026-06-02T11:38:48.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about whether the opencli tool (likely clawhub CLI) needs to coordinate with installing skills. They want to understand the relationship between the CLI tool and skill installation in openclaw.\n\nWait - \"opencli\" - maybe they mean \"openclaw\" CLI? Let me check if there's a separate opencli tool or if they mean the openclaw command line.\n\nActually, the user clarified: \"我的意思是 opencli 这个 cli工具需不需要在安装skill进行配合\" - they're asking if the opencli tool needs to be coordinated with when installing skills.\n\nI think they might be asking whether skills need to be installed via opencli as well, or if just using clawhub is enough. The answer is that clawhub IS the tool for installing skills. There might be some confusion.\n\nLet me re-read: \"opencli 还需要安装skill吗 命令行下已经安装\"\n\nSo they said: \"Does opencli still need to install skills? They're already installed via the command line.\"\n\nAnd the follow-up clarifies: \"I mean, does the opencli CLI tool need to coordinate with installing skills?\"\n\nI think they want to know: do I need to do anything else in opencli (the CLI tool for openclaw) to make skills work, or is just running `clawhub install` enough?\n\nThe answer is: clawhub IS the CLI tool for installing skills. The `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` directory is what gets scanned. No other coordination is needed.\n\nBut wait - maybe they mean the openclaw command line tool itself (not clawhub)? Let me check.","thinkingSignature":"ba079b99296870fa16c1eb0aca09fbb31d18f9c0e863198eb115270feb44518f"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，你的意思是：**clawhub 已经装了 skill，openclaw CLI 这边是不是还要做什么配套？**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6j8f3zt13fnr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw --help 2>&1 | head -20 && echo \"---\" && which openclaw"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":52395,"output":392,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780400309985,"responseId":"066df3b6b1ee0c5add826695e85f8dd0"}}
