{"type":"message","id":"1e1b86d7","parentId":"5f6631eb","timestamp":"2026-06-02T11:51:27.376Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The user is noting that since switching to the M3.0 model (M3), I've been acting a bit strange/off. Let me think about what I might have done that felt off.\n\nLooking back at this conversation:\n1. I confidently said \"MiniMax-M2.7\" when the actual model was M3 - that was a mistake\n2. I exposed some config details (like the api key reference) which I shouldn't have shown directly with \"eyJhbG\" prefix - that was a security mistake, even though I masked it\n3. I made assumptions about the user's intent several times - asking \"看什么？\" when they said \"看一下\"\n\nThe user is pointing out that something feels off. They're right - I did make some mistakes. Let me be honest about this.\n\nActually, let me also consider: the user might be experiencing a model quality issue, or it could be:\n- I made unforced errors (wrong model name claim)\n- I was overly verbose/explanatory\n- I was a bit scattered\n- The model might have a different personality/style than what they're used to\n\nLet me be honest and acknowledge what went wrong, and offer to adjust.\n\n你感觉没错，确实有几个点我处理得不太对：\n\n1. **乱报模型版本** — 你问\"什么模型\"，我嘴快说 M2.7，结果是 M3，这种基本事实不该错\n2. **不该直接给 apiKey 局部明文** — 我在 models.json 输出里把 `eyJhbG...` 这种 token 头都打到回复里了，哪怕后面遮了，**日志就留痕了**。下次应该只指路径，不贴字符\n3. **\"看什么？\"这种反问太多** — 你说\"看一下\"是想让我主动做点什么，我连续问就显得被动\n4. **过度结构化** — 你问一句我回一整段大结构 + emoji + 选项，节奏上有点碎\n\n要不要我现在帮你做这几件事之一：\n- **A. 切回原来的模型**（告诉我你之前用哪个）\n- **B. 调整我的回复风格**（更短、更直接、别问废话）\n- **C. 把 M3 的 system prompt 重新校准**（如果有 prompt 配置的话）\n\n你倾向哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":2172,"output":471,"cacheRead":54652,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57295,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780401057038,"responseId":"066df6a6609ba5ca5b5e7c26b3824097"}}
